<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="HappyFlower" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">說起來，<delay20 /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有聽說過<delay8 />
表情<delay8 />這種東西嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比如說高興或開心的時候，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以像這樣擺動身體<delay20 />
來表現自己的心情喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎麼樣？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是不是比只用說的<delay8 />
更能表達出自己的心情呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想表現自己的心情時，<delay8 />只要按下<colour id="1" /><colour id="65535" />，<delay20 />
