<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很簡單吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />表情還有很多<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其他的種類，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也會先跟島上的大家說，<delay8 />
請他們教你自己會的<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其他表情，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="Thinking" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀？<delay20 />嗯<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天<delay8 />我本來打算要教你<delay8 />
做個新的表情的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過我到底想教你哪個表情呀？<delay frames="40" />
奇怪了，<delay20 />我剛才明明還記得的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay8 />你覺得剛才的「思考中」怎麼樣呢？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個表情很適合用在<delay8 />
想事情的時候吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="Sighing" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />怎麼樣？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有好好活用<delay8 />表情嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看你這反應<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是想學學<delay8 />新的表情吧？<delay frames="40" />
那麼，<delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也不能讓你失望！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想想……<delay20 />該教什麼才好呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
嗯<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒辦法！<delay frames="40" />今天<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像沒那個心情<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><tag a="10" b="12" /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><colour id="4" /><size value="150" />唉～～～～<size value="100" /><colour id="65535" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />你問剛才那是什麼？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是「嘆氣」的表情喔。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不嫌棄的話，要不要試試看？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="Shocked" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵！<delay20 />可能有點突然，<delay frames="30" />
不過，<tag a="110" b="10" />的表情講座<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要開始了喔！<pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
你是不是<delay20 />也常遇到覺得驚訝<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />或被嚇一跳的時候呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天就讓我來教你<delay8 />
最適合這種時候使用的表情吧！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比如說<delay8 />像這樣<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什麼！<delay20 />你說<colour id="3" />豆狸<colour id="65535" />的店<delay8 />
等一下要舉辦特價拍賣！？<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看，<delay20 />這樣是不是就有被嚇一跳的感覺呢？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你遇到什麼驚訝的事，<delay20 />
就用用看這個「驚！」的表情吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="Silent" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay20 />
等一下，我有件事想問你！<pageBreak />你呀<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />吃了我的<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />對吧？<delay20 />
你老實跟我說，<delay8 />我不會生氣的！<pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒有啦，說笑的而已～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我剛才呢，<delay8 />就是用眼神逼迫對方做出反應，<delay20 />
這也就是「瞪」的表情喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />秘訣就是用看透對方內心一般的眼神，<delay20 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />用力瞪著對方<tag a="110" b="0" />！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請你一定要試試看喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="Love" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來也差不多可以<delay8 />
拿出我的壓箱寶，<delay frames="40" />
教你「喜歡」這個表情了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這很適合用在表現陶醉到忘我，<delay20 />
或是感覺超幸福的時候喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想想，<delay20 />說到最近發生的好事<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak />就是我終於得到了<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一直很想要的衣服<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />你看，<delay8 />就像我剛才那樣。<delay8 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當你沉浸在自己的世界時，<delay8 />
就很適合用這個表情喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
